@startuml kv_client_deploy_interaction
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam roundcorner 8
skinparam defaultFontName "SansSerif"

title KVC 部署与交互（简图）

rectangle "业务进程 / 计算节点" as APP {
  component "KVC SDK\n(KVClient)" as SDK
}

rectangle "数据面：KVC Worker 集群" as WORKERS {
  component "Worker A" as WA
  component "Worker B" as WB
}

cloud "控制面：etcd\n(服务发现 / 租约)" as ETCD

SDK --> WA : 读写 RPC、心跳
SDK --> WB : 切流后 RPC、心跳
WA --> ETCD : 注册 / 续租
WB --> ETCD : 注册 / 续租
SDK ..> ETCD : 发现 Worker\n(经客户端库，非直连业务代码)

note bottom of SDK
  典型交互：SDK 持当前 Worker 连接；
  心跳失败则换 Worker；etcd 侧完成成员与隔离。
end note

@enduml
